{"tid":245931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好廢呀我","createTime":"2017-05-16T15:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T15:52:19.000Z","uid":4936,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb80950d2ea56cbb9ee7f98722130a2b854b2350","tid":245931,"uid":4936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:23:46.000Z","msg":"點解我咁廢 <br />\n點解我咁垃圾<br />\n點解我好懶<br />\n仲要明知道自己咁懶都唔肯改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你咁好嘅人應該值得更好嘅女仔同你一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而唔係我咁樣嘅臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同我一齊根本就係資源錯配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日又因為我懶而搞到你嬲 你都係為我好 點解我就係唔肯去做<br />\n不如由得我一個算啦<br />\n好似我咁廢嘅人唔配同你一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7eb8f6bf73755640806165067ef36b4a9e829a","tid":245931,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:24:44.000Z","msg":"乜鳩"},{"pid":"580aeb38f4d8fd089af2b6e2983bc40d5133ffbb","tid":245931,"uid":4936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:25:26.000Z","msg":"臭閪港女"},{"pid":"b8dfe1852b64e99b0bfd35dbaf39d081616a1f4c","tid":245931,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"K"},{"pid":"ca2a892919024fc866266a3f86717892d887eaeb","tid":245931,"uid":4936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知我做乜鳩"},{"pid":"60149a4f2fa431b1a046440237f3622fc8ef057a","tid":245931,"uid":4936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>K</blockquote><br />\n多謝你睇我鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"